I'll be the referee

44
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,600
I said I'd chop you first

45
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,040
Tired of living, are you?

46
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:49,680
Can't wait to

47
