49
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,000
Don't just stand there!

50
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,200
Get him

51
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,400
Hey kid

52
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,720
Writing, are you?

53
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,240
Great

54
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:23,400
This...

55
