63
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,520
Give me a break. Give me a break.

64
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,560
Are you two done yet?

65
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,520
Almost

66
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,400
I've already spotted his weakness

67
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:28,640
Me too

68
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,040
I'm about to spot yours too

69
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:36,880
How about I take over?

70
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,000
If you...

71
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,920
If you put it that way

72
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,320
