73
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,400
I love hitting women the most

74
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,000
Then let's begin

75
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,800
Congratulations on your total victory, General

76
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,720
Trifles, trifles

77
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,840
Drink tea, drink tea

78
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,840
