95
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,520
There should be a bonfire,

96
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,320
dancing, drinking, and meat.

97
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,320
Given our village's current situation,

98
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,400
as you all know,

99
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,640
apart from crayfish,

100
