103
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,400
I'll treat you all to it.

104
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,680
Don't just drink.

105
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,680
We should toast to something.

106
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:37,560
All right.

107
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,480
This bowl is to Aqin.

108
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,440
To her company on this journey.

109
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:02,920
Cheers.

110
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,760
Then this bowl of mine,

111
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:05,960
is to Yu Tong.

112
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:08,360
Because she was on this journey,

113
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,680
