114
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,840
I toast this bowl to you.

115
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,440
This wine is very precious.

116
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,120
Brother Wei Qiao,

117
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,240
